//Mediastinal vessels - Aorta

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 09 of Cardio MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Mediastinal vessels' from the dropdown menu

When I select 'Aorta' radio button
Then 'Extension' checkbox is enabled
And 'Stenosis' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Extension' checkbox
Then 'Elongation' radio button is enabled
And 'Aneurysm' radio button is enabled
And 'Aortic root' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ascending aorta' checkbox is enabled
And 'Aortic arch' checkbox is enabled
And 'Descending aorta' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Aorta descendens' checkbox
Then 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled

When I select 'Stenosis' checkbox
Then 'Aortic stenosis / aortic coarctation' radio button is enabled
And 'Supra valvular' radio button is enabled
